    "body": "I'd be ok with adding withdrawal logic back in, and just setting the *deletion* time to infinity.\r\n\r\nWe should also add a receipt tree that includes withdrawal receipts (potentially doable as easily as just storing in the state a list of withdrawals in the last block, completely overwriting it each block, though this would make processing harder; the alternative is to have a `receipt_root` in the block, which would allow more unified receipt processing code on the beacon chain and the shards).",
